method 1) naive O(mn) i.e copy a array onto arraylist u and then search for every element from the other array, if present do not copy, if not 		copy

method 2) sort and do like union for sorted array
	
method 3) sort a smaller array and put into into arraylist, now check for every element of larger array if it is present in smaller array, if 		not add

method 4) hashing, add a array onto hash table and U, and check by iterating the second array if the value is present ignore else add into U
